#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.41"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.41:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.41:0.2"
msgid "5. Jarāvagga"
msgstr "5. Old Age"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 41. Jarādhammasutta → jarāsuttaṃ (bj) | jarā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.41:0.3"
msgid "41. Jarādhammasutta"
msgstr "41. Old Age"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.41:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn48.41:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati pubbārāme migāramātupāsāde."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in the Eastern Monastery, "
"the stilt longhouse of Migāra’s mother."

msgctxt "sn48.41:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito "
"pacchātape nisinno hoti piṭṭhiṃ otāpayamāno."
msgstr ""
"Then in the late afternoon, the Buddha came out of retreat and sat warming "
"his back in the last rays of the sun."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.41:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā bhagavato gattāni pāṇinā anomajjanto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, and while massaging the "
"Buddha’s limbs he said:"

msgctxt "sn48.41:2.2"
msgid "“acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante."
msgstr "“It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing,"

msgctxt "sn48.41:2.3"
msgid ""
"Na cevaṃ dāni, bhante, bhagavato tāva parisuddho chavivaṇṇo pariyodāto, "
"sithilāni ca gattāni sabbāni valiyajātāni, purato pabbhāro ca kāyo, dissati "
"ca indriyānaṃ aññathattaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"how the complexion of your skin is no longer pure and bright. Your limbs are "
"flaccid and wrinkled, and your body is stooped. And it’s apparent that there "
"has been a deterioration in your faculties"

msgctxt "sn48.41:2.4"
msgid ""
"cakkhundriyassa sotindriyassa ghānindriyassa jivhindriyassa kāyindriyassā”ti."
msgstr "of eye, ear, nose, tongue, and body.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.217"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.41:3.1"
msgid "“Evañhetaṃ, ānanda, hoti—"
msgstr "“That’s how it is, Ānanda."

msgctxt "sn48.41:3.2"
msgid "jarādhammo yobbaññe, byādhidhammo ārogye, maraṇadhammo jīvite."
msgstr ""
"When young you’re liable to grow old; when healthy you’re liable to get sick;"
" and when alive you’re liable to die."

msgctxt "sn48.41:3.3"
msgid ""
"Na ceva tāva parisuddho hoti chavivaṇṇo pariyodāto, sithilāni ca honti "
"gattāni sabbāni valiyajātāni, purato pabbhāro ca kāyo, dissati ca indriyānaṃ "
"aññathattaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"The complexion of the skin is no longer pure and bright. The limbs are "
"flaccid and wrinkled, and the body is stooped. And it’s apparent that there "
"has been a deterioration in the faculties"

msgctxt "sn48.41:3.4"
msgid ""
"cakkhundriyassa sotindriyassa ghānindriyassa jivhindriyassa kāyindriyassā”ti."
msgstr "of eye, ear, nose, tongue, and body.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.41:4.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "sn48.41:4.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā ca sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā:"
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.41:5.1"
msgid "“Dhī taṃ jammi jare atthu,"
msgstr "“Curse this wretched old age,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn48.41:5.2"
msgid "dubbaṇṇakaraṇī jare;"
msgstr "which makes you so ugly."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn48.41:5.3"
msgid "Tāva manoramaṃ bimbaṃ,"
msgstr "That’s how much this delightful puppet"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn48.41:5.4"
msgid "jarāya abhimadditaṃ."
msgstr "is ground down by old age."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.41:6.1"
msgid "Yopi vassasataṃ jīve,"
msgstr "Even if you live for a hundred years,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: sopi maccuparāyaṇo → sabbe maccuparāyanā (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn48.41:6.2"
msgid "sopi maccuparāyaṇo;"
msgstr "you’ll still end up dying."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn48.41:6.3"
msgid "Na kiñci parivajjeti,"
msgstr "Death spares no-one,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn48.41:6.4"
msgid "sabbamevābhimaddatī”ti."
msgstr "but crushes all underfoot.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.41:6.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
